{"tid":1720062,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗：警方缺人手　難實施宵禁","createTime":"2019-11-14T08:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T08:43:41.000Z","uid":156509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"429910f849b7420a337a0c642772bfd58182b037","tid":1720062,"uid":156509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T08:43:41.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】<br />\n　　全國人大常委譚耀宗表示，不清楚政府是否討論過實施宵禁令，但認為以警方現時的人手，即使實施宵禁令亦無能力執行。<br />\n<br />\n　　被問到駐港解放軍會以否義工身分清除路障，譚耀宗指應由其他政府部門加派人手清理，又指出動解放軍是需要很多準備。對於有指港澳辦主任張曉明本來計劃來港，宣講解讀四中全會，譚耀宗表示現時非最適合時候要集中止暴制亂，會再作安排。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=369861&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369861%26refer%3DShare&d=kXTsEwo%2F%2B0BMNdh3S%2FGVc4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=5fea3b3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D369861%26refer%3DShare&h=b8c09f61\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=369861&amp;refer=Share</a>"}]}